<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0" /> 
<title>编辑收货信息</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/main.css" />
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/lib/require.js" data-main="js/conf/addressConf"></script>
</head>

<body data-tracker-name="address" style="background:#FAFAFA;">
<div class="wrap">
    <ul class="addressWrap">
        <li><div class="addressBox"><input type="text" id="name" maxlength="20" placeholder="姓名" /></div></li>
        <li><div class="addressBox"><input type="tel" id="tel" placeholder="手机号" maxlength="11" /></div></li>
        <li><div class="addressBox"><input type="tel" id="qq" placeholder="QQ号" maxlength="12" /></div></li>
        <li><div class="addressBox"><input type="text" id="area" placeholder="所在地区" /></div></li>
        <li><div class="addressBox"><input type="text" id="addr" maxlength="128" placeholder="详细地址" /></div></li>
    </ul>
    <div id="addressTips">该收货地址是默认收货地址，修改单个订单地址，请在订单列表中点击“修改地址”按钮！</div>
    <div id="setDefault"><span></span><label>设为默认地址</label><p>设为默认地址后，下次提交订单会默认使用该地址</p></div>
    <div id="SetDefaultAddr">
        <input type="checkbox" id="setDef" value="false" />
        <input type="hidden" id="userId" />
        <input type="hidden" id="province" value="" />
        <input type="hidden" id="city" value="" />
        <input type="hidden" id="county" value="" />
        <input type="hidden" id="areaTemp" value="" />
    </div>
    <div class="addressBtn" id="addrBtnWrap"><a id="SubmitAddr">完成</a></div>
</div>
</body>
</html>